('Bureaucracy.es', 'Gestor', 'Your guide through the Spanish bureaucracy. Immigration solicitors and gestors specializing in Spanish visas for expats, digital nomads, and retirees. Services include Non-Lucrative Visa, Digital Nomad Visa, Student Visa, visa renewals, and Spanish citizenship applications. Features a secure online dashboard and mobile app for document upload, digital signatures, and real-time progress tracking. Free consultations available. Transparent pricing with no hidden fees - Non-Lucrative Visa €999, Digital Nomad Visa €1,399, Student Visa €499. Family discounts available. Official translations included in service fees. English-speaking team with exceptional approval record. Bureaucracy International Group Ltd. registered with Dutch Chamber of Commerce (KVK 88274276). Featured on CNN. Also offers B2B solutions including white-label visa services and affiliate programs.', 'Online service (location-indexed; serves all Spain)', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', NULL, 'hola@bureaucracy.es', 'https://bureaucracy.es', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW());
